N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 263.10 - Singular/plural use of terms

State Regulations

Any term used in the singular in these rules also
encompasses the plural of that term. For example, the terms
employer
or
labor organization
encompass the
terms
employers
or
labor
organizations. Notes
